_sText: A police car prefab using the black de_nuke car. I made this car for a map I'm working on, af_omega. The car is free to be used by anyone, and free to be re-distributed so long as you keep the included text document with it. Thanks to scytha -- I liked his police car but wanted something more so I heavily modified it. This version only kept the letters he had, nothing else, and those were also modified. Anyone who intends to use the prefab should read the .txt file.
